SDL for TI-Nspire calculators (version 0.1.4 beta)
=============================

Ported by Christoffer Rehn (christoffer.rehn@telenet.be)

Note: Ndless 3.1 is required to use SDL on the TI-Nspire calculators.

How to use:
Copy the include/ and lib/ folders to the Ndless sdk/ folder. Adapt the
Makefile.sample file to your need.

For more information have a look at the thread on Omnimaga:
http://www.omnimaga.org/index.php?topic=12378.0